[30;1m182 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m183 | [0m[35mIn this directive, we are **constructing MyST {term}`AST`** using the directive's argument.[0m
[30;1m184 | [0m[35mMyST AST is the structure built when you "build a MyST site".[0m
[30;1m185 | [0m[35mAbove, we're defining two MyST nodes: a `paragraph` node (`type: "paragraph"`) and a `text` node (`t[0m
[30;1m186 | [0m[35m[0m
[30;1m187 | [0m[35mFinally, we **return an array of MyST nodes**.[0m
[30;1m188 | [0m[35mThis array is what will be inserted into the document when the directive is run.[0m
